Distribution .
Culex acharistus
is known from Brazil , Chile , Argentina (
Knight & Stone, 1977
) and Colombia (
Bram, 1967
). In Argentina it is recorded from Córdoba, Corrientes, Jujuy, Neuquén, Río Negro, Tucumán, Chubut (
Campos & Maciá, 1998
) and Buenos Aires (
Rossi, 2000
) provinces.
